CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Stretching for miles to the west, mountains tower as far as the eye can see.
Just a few more hundred feet above, the snow-topped peak stretches into the
clouds. A small opening in the mountain has been revealed as the summer heat
melts the glittering ice. To the east, the deepening fog smears the view.
The ledge around the mountain continues above and below.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MOUNTAIN
DAY_LIGHT
EXIT SE 633
EXIT SW 635
EXIT ABOVE 2108
