NUMBER 1252
NAME Outer Cave
ASTRAL
DARKNESS
CALL 33
MONSTER_GROUP 51
MINEC
*DESCRIPTION_START
The sloping floor of this large cave is well-worn by the constant tread of
enormous heavy feet. The giants that reside here apparently use this area
as their dumping grounds. Great piles of refuse are strewn about, their
stench mingling with the fresher air that occasionally wafts in when the
magical wall briefly fades away to allow someone to enter. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 1253
