; huge reeking pile
EXTEND 1 of carelessly discarded garbage
PUT 1 880 ADJ1=249
; putrid intestines (in garbage pile)

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Precisely shaped blocks of timeworn gray granite line the edges of the arch.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Not having regular access to the outside of the mountain proper, the giants
have taken to using this outermost cave as a place to put their refuse. Old
bones, hides, offal, and vegetable matter mingle with useless bits of broken
glass and metal in a large, disgusting mess.
*DESCRIPTION_END

