NUMBER 1255
NAME Smoky Cave
ASTRAL
DARKNESS
CALL 33
BUY_SKINS
MONSTER_GROUP 51
*DESCRIPTION_START
A barrage of smells and sounds assail the senses as one enters this huge
communal eating area. A massive iron cauldron hangs over an equally enormous
firepit, mingling the smells of cooking meat and broth with the acrid tang
of woodsmoke. Stirring the contents, and occasionally tossing in a handful of
whatever ingredient strikes her fancy, is a towering giantess with a stern
expression on her craggy features. Those who are hungry bring tub-sized bowls
for her to fill, while other giants returning from hunting or foraging
replenish the stocks with what they have gathered.
*DESCRIPTION_END
