MONSTER_GROUP 51
*DESCRIPTION_START
A large set of iron double doors dominates the room. Up to within fifty feet
of the doors are the normal signs of the everyday life of the giants, but the
area is utterly clear for the remaining distance. Even dust has failed to take
hold upon their softly burnished surface, nor has time or dampness marred them
with corrosion. The doors are set directly into rock by a crafter of fantastic
skill, the hinges hidden within the living stone to either side.
*DESCRIPTION_END
