*DESCRIPTION_START
An inch of crystal clear water covers the entire floor. It flows up the
walls to the domed ceiling, only to shower down again in a continuous
cycle of rainfall. In the middle of the room is a altar, with tiny azure
bolts of electricity that arc across its surface yet do not touch upon
the water on the floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
